name: Voyeur
Lore: 'As there are very few local authorities on Dagobah, peeping Nav Computers can get away with just about anything.',
Text: 'Name an Interrupt card. Opponent must reveal entire Used Pile, without shuffling. Then you choose:USED: Opponent must lose 1 Force for each copy of that Interrupt found there.LOST: Each copy of that interrupt found there is lost.',
